Interface SshAuthenticator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Authenticator

    public interface SshAuthenticator
extends Authenticator
    Implementations of this interface authenticate SSH connections given appropriate credentials.

    This class participates in the visitor pattern with SshCredential.
